name: CTA
body:
## Easy CTA

### CTA should be visually striking with copy that compels you to click the offer

Looking for cta design? We are easy to understand and clear about CTA. Be sure to state exactly what the visitor will get if they click on the CTA and go to the landing page

Our features:
* A/B Testing
* Form Conversion
* Form Optimization
* Branch logic
* Payment integration
* Third party integration
* Push notifications
* Multiple language support
* Conditional logic
* Validation rules
* Server rules
* Custom reports

### CTAs come in all forms, sizes, and colors.

Options abound for every situation, whether you are attracting leads or customers or want to draw guests to an event, we are ready to customize your [CTA](https://formtitan.com/OptimizationTips/Call-To-Action-CTA-Improve-Conversion-Rates).

Happy CTA!
